{"tid":1481114,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"我大哥正一傻鳩","createTime":"2019-08-17T14:48:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T01:57:24.000Z","uid":162567,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d7eb5297ee96c3d60cae3fdaca54d6026523a3d3","tid":1481114,"uid":162567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T14:48:48.000Z","msg":"早幾個星期，我二哥約左agent睇樓，但業主強硬唔減價，呎價都萬8蚊一呎，300呎一房，約540萬<br />\n咁agent問佢新樓有冇興趣，佢咪話睇下，4叔樓黎既，睇完示範單位係好靚，位置都唔差，但開放式黎，但呎價要3萬蚊一呎，但得200呎，埋單要600萬<br />\n根住我二哥當然要諗諗，貴左仲細左，但我大哥好似經紀上身，話呢層樓好，位置好，總價都係比之前貴少少，又近返市區，乜乜物物，好似佢有佣分咁，加埋個真agent講講講，二哥好似受到疲勞轟炸咁，當然佢好醒，冇簽到就同agent講話要諗下計下先<br />\n我心諗，大哥做乜鳩，層樓又唔係落你名，供又唔係你供，佣你又冇份收，做乜好似推二哥去死咁，3萬蚊呎買濕鳩開放式，正傻鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d951ec5b178c36accd889318c70c34adc5a6fa22","tid":1481114,"uid":167419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫大哥自己買"},{"pid":"1c769ae0d9a51f1726f833aea597b276b8eb4b63","tid":1481114,"uid":129186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:29:38.000Z","msg":"兄弟反目<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c3af5ffb0c9da682458cb0aab2677ffaf3e1673","tid":1481114,"uid":162567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d951ec5b178c36accd889318c70c34adc5a6fa22","tid":1481114,"uid":167419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T15:24:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />叫大哥自己買"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T16:30:42.000Z","msg":"大哥成閪日都唔用腦做事，點先可以屌醒佢"},{"pid":"393ebf9d116400aa56fe6cf162b627fd3a423739","tid":1481114,"uid":19725,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"5c3af5ffb0c9da682458cb0aab2677ffaf3e1673","tid":1481114,"uid":162567,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d951ec5b178c36accd889318c70c34adc5a6fa22","tid":1481114,"uid":167419,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"ci